name: Yu Yu Hakusho
overview: After a selfless act costs him his life, teen delinquent Yusuke Urameshi is chosen as a Spirit Detective to investigate cases involving rogue yokai.
tagline: Ready for an epic yokai battle?

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Awakening to a startling truth, Yusuke is greeted by a Spirit World guide. Meanwhile, malevolent otherworldly forces unleash chaos in the Human World.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Rogue yokai steal three dangerous objects. As Yusuke grapples with his new powers, children playing at a park mysteriously collapse to the ground.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Charged with reclaiming the final dangerous object, Yusuke infiltrates a mansion. Later, Koenma assigns him a powerful mentor to help with training.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: On Kubikukuri Island, Yusuke's crew disperse to confront their foes. Locked in a prison cell, Keiko encounters Yukina and devises an escape plan.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Yusuke finally comes face to face with Toguro and uncovers the shocking truth. Koenma confronts Sakyo as the Demon World rapidly opens up.
